<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>阿育王舍利地圖</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: #f5f5f5;
      font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .container {
      width: 80vw;
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 2em auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .intro-card, .card {
      width: 100%;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      padding: 2em;
      margin-bottom: 1.5em;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.2em;
    }
    .card-title {
      font-size: 2em;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 0.5em;
    }
    .map-container iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 500px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro-card">
      《大唐西域記．卷一》釋迦如來滅度之後，阿育王遵佛遺教，取八塔真身舍利，分為八萬四千，遍於天下建塔供養。
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-title">《大唐西域記》阿育王舍利地圖</div>
      <div class="map-container">
        <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=1wiiaH0G6M1fEy0OftYkKkeey6pB7PHo&ehbc=2E312F" allowfullscreen title="阿育王舍利地圖"></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
